synopsis:
A collection of short stories:

1. Hotaru (螢) — published in English as «Firefly» by Harvill Secker in «Blind Willow, Sleeping Woman» in 2006;
2. Naya o yaku (納屋を焼く) — published in English as «Barn Burning» by Knopf in «The Elephant Vanishes» in March 31, 1993;
3. Odoru kobito (踊る小人) — published in English as «The Dancing Dwarf» by Knopf in «The Elephant Vanishes» in March 31, 1993;
4. Mekurayanagi to nemuru onna (めくらやなぎと眠る女), published in English as «Blind Willow, Sleeping Woman» by Harvill Secker in «Blind Willow, Sleeping Woman» in 2006;
5. Mittsu no Doitsu gensō (三つのドイツ幻想).
